I want to study social work to help people in trouble. I want to work with the Division of Family and Children Services. This group helps children who have been hurt or neglected. They also help families in trouble. I can give the following values to the social work field: 1) help others, 2) respect, 3) be honest, 4) work hard to help people and myself, and 5) be a good person.

I have always wanted to help people. But I was not sure what job I wanted to do. In high school and college, I saw people run away from their problems. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. I saw this and decided to study psychology. After I graduated from college, I took a break. One day, I visited a friend who had a 16-year-old boy who was very nervous. He was there to escape his bad parents. The next day, I went to his parents' house to help. I told the police that I had studied psychology in college. They asked me to talk to the parents. I asked them about their son. They seemed nervous and made excuses. This made me think about how I can help children like him.

Another important value for social work is fairness. We say that every person is important, but we do not always act like it. We say we are sorry when someone dies, but we do not try to be different from others. I am a unique person. I do not like to limit myself to be like everyone else. In high school and college, I protested against unfairness. I colored my hair in bright colors, wore clothes that fit my personality, and stood up against racism and unfair treatment.

I believe in fairness and will continue to stand up against unfairness.

This paper looks at two ways to understand a problem called insomnia. One way is called the biological model. It looks at things like genes, which we get from our parents, and health problems. The other way is the sociocultural model. It looks at how the world around us affects our sleep.

The biological model says that our genes and health can affect our sleep. Some research looked at mice and found a special group of cells in the brain that help us sleep and wake up. These cells have something called orexin. If these cells are active, we are awake. If they are not, we sleep. A study found that a special chemical can help these cells work better and make us sleep more.

The sociocultural model says that the world around us can affect our sleep. If we inherit a problem with our genes, we may have trouble sleeping. This can make it hard for us to do everyday things like go to school or work. We may have trouble paying attention and doing tasks that are boring.

Insomnia can be a problem because we can't sleep well. There are different kinds of insomnia. One kind is called primary insomnia. This is when we have trouble sleeping for at least a month. Another kind is called hypersomnia. This is when we have trouble staying awake for a long time.

The biological model is important because it can help us understand why we sleep or don't sleep. If we know what is causing our insomnia, we can try to fix it. The sociocultural model is also important because it can help us understand how the world around us can affect our sleep. If we know what is causing our insomnia, we can try to change our environment to help us sleep better.

This paper talks about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). It explains what CAPD is. Then it talks about how to diagnose the disorder. Finally, it says how teachers can help students with CAPD in a regular classroom.

CAPD is a problem with the brain. Our brain takes in sound and uses it to understand what we hear. People with CAPD can hear normally. But their brain has a hard time using sound to understand things. It is not a hearing problem. It is a problem with how the brain works.

The first time people talked about CAPD was in the 1950s. They called it "auditory imperception". They were studying children with speech problems. In 1954, an Italian team started making tests for these children. In 1961, a scientist named Kimura made a test to see how well the brain works when listening to two sounds at the same time.

CAPD causes many problems. People with CAPD may have trouble hearing where sound comes from. They may have trouble hearing two sounds at the same time. They may not be able to recognize sound patterns. They may not be able to understand when someone's voice changes. They may have trouble hearing one sound when another sound is louder. They may not be able to understand the order of sounds.

To diagnose CAPD, doctors and other experts use special tests. They watch how the person behaves and gives them tasks to do. These tasks may include listening to sounds and choosing the right one. They may use questionnaires and observe how the person reacts to different sounds. There is no one good test for CAPD. Doctors use different tests to try to find out if someone has CAPD.

Teachers can help students with CAPD in a regular classroom. They can give them extra help when they are listening to the teacher. They can help the student when they are in a noisy place. They can also give the student a quiet area to work in.

The play Twelfth Night says people use disguise to trick others. But this can be bad. If you wear a disguise, you can lose yourself. One problem is that you may become alone. People may not like you when they find out you tricked them. 

You have to choose between being safe and keeping friends. Some people will not be mad when they find out they were tricked. But others will be very upset. 

The play talks about a woman named Viola. She wears a disguise to protect herself. She is a woman, but she dresses as a man. This helps her, but it also makes her lonely. She misses her female friends. 

Viola is so good at her disguise that a woman named Olivia falls in love with her. But Olivia also falls in love with a man named Sebastian. This shows that sometimes people do not know what they really want. 

Some people think that Viola helps Olivia and a man named Orsino see their true feelings. They may have feelings they do not know about. Viola's disguise makes them think about these feelings. But some people think Olivia is just pretending to love Viola. She is making fun of people who judge others based on how they look. 

This is shown when Olivia stops loving Viola and starts to see her as a sister, not a lover. Olivia does this easily and quickly.

The German colonial government was very cruel. It is especially known for its treatment of the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. But this is not the whole story. German colonies were different from each other. Their leaders made different rules. Education in the colonies was also different. When the British took over German East Africa in 1919, they found many Africans who were educated and could read. The Germans did a good job in Kamerun and other colonies. But in South West Africa, the government did very little to help the local people get an education. Missionary groups did some, but not much. The government, however, spent a lot on educating European settlers. They built schools for Europeans and helped the missionary schools. These decisions had a big effect on South West Africa, even after the Germans left. While many Africans in other German colonies were educated, most people in South West Africa were not. 

Various factors caused these differences. This paper will look at these factors and learn more about the attitudes of the settlers and the colonial government towards the local people.

There are many books about education in the German colonies. Most of these books are in German and were written a long time ago. They mostly describe the education systems in the colonies. Later books compared the education systems of different colonies and looked at specific parts of education. These studies showed that the education systems in different colonies were very different. A scientist named Cohen studied education in South West Africa and East Africa. He compared their education systems and said that the number of European settlers in South West Africa was the main reason for its differences.

South West Africa had a good climate, but much of the land is desert. Many Europeans moved there because it was a good place to live. By 1913, 15,000 Europeans lived in South West Africa. Only 5,336 Europeans lived in the colony with the next largest number of settlers.

Popular music has changed a lot over the last 100 years. Many different kinds of music exist now. We can't list them all. Some kinds of music, like rock, country, jazz, and folk, have many smaller kinds inside them. One kind of music, Heavy Metal, is very popular. It is very expressive. It shows many different feelings, but most are sad or dark. This is because people who make Heavy Metal music like to express strong emotions. Heavy Metal music is also very diverse. People started creating their own kinds of Heavy Metal music quickly after it began. This led to many more kinds of music, and it continues today.

Now, it is hard to know what Heavy Metal music is. It has taken ideas from other kinds of music. But it started from somewhere. To understand Heavy Metal music, we need to know what it is and why it exists.

Heavy Metal music is about darkness. It is loud and has strong beats. People who make Heavy Metal music are very good at playing their instruments. Heavy Metal music often talks about dark things, like drugs and sadness. Many people who make Heavy Metal music were influenced by dark ideas in the past. They also took some ideas from the Romantic Era. This era was known for its sad and emotional music. Some lyrics of Heavy Metal songs show how dark and sad the music can be.

The Beatles wrote a song called Helter Skelter. It is considered one of the first Heavy Metal songs. The song is about the darker side of life. It was a reaction to another song by the Rolling Stones, which was also very dark. The Beatles wanted to show that they could make music as heavy and dark as the Rolling Stones.

Henri Rousseau was a famous painter. He made paintings about his dreams. His painting "The Dream" is from 1910. It shows a woman in a dream. This woman is in a beautiful place. Rousseau's painting also shows his own dreams and goals. He wanted to be known as a good painter. He wanted his work to be liked by other artists and people who love art.

Rousseau's dream was hard to achieve. He had to decide: should he paint like other artists? Or should he be different? This is a difficult choice. Rousseau was born in a town in France in 1844. His father was a metal worker. Rousseau grew up without learning art. He worked for the government until he was 40. Then he started painting. This was very late in life.

Rousseau's life changed when his wife died. He was very sad. He had one child, a daughter named Julia. He wanted to feel better. So, he started painting. His paintings are about everyday people like him. They are not fancy like paintings by other artists.

Rousseau wanted the art world to like him. This was hard because many artists were better known than him. They started painting early and were very good. Rousseau started painting late and was not as good. But he kept working. Finally, people began to like his art. Another artist, Matisse, was also making a name for himself. They were different artists. Matisse wanted to be good, but Rousseau wanted to be accepted.

Many people think that ethics and art are closely connected. They believe that truth and beauty are the same thing. This is what John Keats says in his poem "Ode on a Grecian Urn". He says, "Beauty is truth. Truth is beauty." This idea is important because we learn many things in life, but we know that art and ethics are special. We understand them without being taught.

We try to explain why art is good and why actions are moral. But we cannot fully explain them. Our explanations are like a map that shows us the way, but we cannot see the destination. When we talk about art, we use words like "beauty" and "truth". But in the end, we say "there is something about it" that we cannot explain.

Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that cannot be said any other way." This means that art and ethics are special because we cannot fully explain them. They are like a secret that we cannot tell. This is what makes them powerful. 

We experience ethics and art at a deep level. This level is like a feeling that we cannot explain. This is why they are connected. When we read a book or look at a painting, we feel something that we cannot explain. This is the connection between ethics and art.

The connection is stronger when it comes to literature. Literature is special because it has a moral quality. It teaches us values that are important for life. Living is about values, and literature helps us understand them.

Germany is a strong country with its own culture. The culture is the same from the mountains in the south to the Baltic Sea in the north. It is the same culture from the city of Munich to the city of Kiel. The culture is the same in the city of Cologne on the Rhine River, and in the city of Dresden on the Elbe River.

Germany has a unique culture. This is because many people from different groups lived in Germany a long time ago. The name "Germany" comes from the group of people known as the Germans. But the word "German" has a long history.

Some people think the name "German" comes from a group of people called the Tungrians. They lived a long time ago and were called Germans. Others think it comes from the word "ger," which is a type of spear used in war. Another idea is that the word "German" comes from the Old Irish word "garim," which means to shout. This could be because the Germans were loud and noisy.

A Roman historian named Tacitus wrote about the origins of the Germans. He said that the Germans were the original people of Germany and that they were not mixed with other people. They lived in a wild and cold country, and it was not a good place to live. So, who would want to leave Rome and come to Germany?

The Romans did not want to live in Germany either. They would sometimes send soldiers to fight in Germany, but they would mostly stay in their own country. The Germanic tribes lived on the border of the Roman Empire and traded with the Romans. They would sell goods and fight in the Roman army.

I looked down.  The scene before me was clear.  But my mind was empty.  I did not think about what I was seeing.  I just saw it.  Thoughts came to me, then went away.  My mind was like a calm water.  It was not thinking.  It was just seeing.

A long time ago, I got a book to help me draw.  It was called The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain.  I wanted to draw since I was six years old.  The book teaches how to see and understand pictures.  One thing it says is to put a square frame around a picture.  This makes a complicated picture simple.

At that moment, I looked at a bowl of fruit in front of me.  I could not put a frame around it in my mind.  I was surprised and amazed.  Artists like Picasso and Monet used different colors in their work.  I wanted to make a picture.  I wanted to call it Work in Brown.

I picked up my pencil.  My hand was ready to draw.  But then I remembered something else I needed to do.  I had to clean the toilet.  The brown waste in the toilet bowl was stuck.  I tried to flush it away.  But it did not go.  I was not happy.  I was frustrated.  I grabbed a mop and tried to get the waste out.  But it was hard.  I had to think and try again.  Finally, I was able to get the waste out of the toilet.

I stood up straight and smiled.  I was able to clean the toilet.  I was proud of myself.  I had worked hard and it was finished.  I was ready to draw now.  I picked up my pencil and began to draw.  I was creating something new and exciting.  I was making art.

Teenagers are dying in car accidents.  Many things cause this problem.  Scientists say one reason is that the teen brain is not ready for the dangers of driving.  Teenagers also have not had much driving experience.  This lack of experience causes many accidents and makes driving more dangerous.

Teenagers are more likely to have car accidents when they drive with their friends.  This is true because many teenagers drive with their friends.  A study showed that the age of the passenger and the number of car accidents are connected.

Some states have rules to help keep teenagers safe.  For example, California has a special license that lets teenagers drive, but limits the hours they can drive and says they cannot have other minors in the car.

But these rules are not enough.  The problem is that young drivers are not ready to drive safely.  A psychologist named Marvin Zuckerman says that 18-year-olds are too young to drive.  He thinks teenagers want to take risks to have fun.  So, it makes sense to wait until they are older before giving them a driver's license.

If we do not change the rules, we will see more car accidents and many people will die.  Many teenagers will start driving soon because the number of teenagers will increase.

We can solve this problem with a simple law.  Schools can teach teenagers how to drive, but no one under 18 can drive.  Teenagers can still get a special permit before they get a regular license.  They will still have to practice driving with an adult for many hours.  This is a simple way to keep teenagers safe.

This idea is not new.  Many people have suggested it before.  A national law would help keep teenagers safe across the country.

The Library of Congress has many old films by Thomas Edison. I watched all 15 trick films made between 1895 and 1901. These films use editing to create illusions. My study of film focused on how most trick films are made and how some of the later films are different.

Most trick films from this time are made in a simple way. The camera does not move. The shots are long or medium shots. The filmmakers use one shot per film. However, some early films do not follow these rules.

One thing that trick films often have in common is that they are filmed inside a set. The camera does not move to follow the actors or objects. This style comes from the theatre and magic shows. Because of this, the actors in trick films can only move side to side. They do not walk towards or away from the camera. In the film "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel" (1900), the actors enter from one side and move back and forth.

Most trick films are long or medium shots. Close-up shots are not used. This is because the theatre and magic shows show the whole performance at the same time. The actors do not move towards the camera, so close-ups do not happen.

Most trick films have one idea per film. This means they are usually short, under a minute. They often focus on simple tricks like magic or disappearing acts. However, one idea in a film can be made up of several shots to create an illusion. In the film "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots" (1895), one shot is actually many shots joined together.

John Taylor was a strong supporter of democracy.  He was a farmer, but his work and a short time in politics made him known for speaking his mind on freedom and government.  Taylor believed in an agricultural way of life.  He thought this way of life was the best.  This idea influenced his ideas about government.

Taylor believed the United States was a great chance to make a perfect system of government.  There was no old tradition to stop the people who made the government.  This allowed the United States to have a system where people could govern themselves.  Taylor believed people have natural rights.  These rights are important for all people and are connected.  If one right is taken away, all rights are harmed.  Taylor thought the government should not have power over these rights.

Taylor said that in the past, strong people and smart people who wanted to harm others were the ones who got ahead.  But in a society, this should not be true.  Taylor wanted a government that understands the good and bad in people.  He believed in two kinds of morality.  He said a good government must protect private property and help farmers.  A good government will work fairly, even if the leaders are not fair.  Taylor believed people are motivated by self-interest.  But self-interest is bad if it hurts others.  A good government must keep people from doing bad things.

Taylor wanted a small government that does not have more powers than the Constitution says it can have.  He did not like a big government because it is expensive and can be cruel.  But he also did not think a simple reading of the Constitution was good.  Without understanding the writers' ideas, this method can be unfair.  Taylor thought the Declaration of Independence was the true document that defines the United States.  This document says the United States is a group of independent states, not one nation.

We look at Figure 17. The number of commuter log submissions fell sharply in the third month of the project. This was not good news. We are not sure why this happened. Winter came to the campus in New England. Fewer people use bicycles or walk to school. This might be the reason for some of the drop. December is the end of the fall semester. People are busy with schoolwork. They may not think about the commuter log. Many students and teachers take a long break in December. They do not need to go to school. Classes start again in late January. But the number of log submissions was still low. We made the Carpool Challenge Week in March. This was a special effort to make people interested in the project again. It helped increase the number of log submissions. We want to keep people excited about the project. We face two problems. Some people naturally lose interest over time. Also, students and teachers have breaks from school. This makes it hard to keep people interested. 

Another problem is that many people like to drive their cars. This is a part of our culture. We need to give rewards to people who use alternative ways to commute. We gave gift cards to local stores and restaurants. This helped some. But we thought it would be good to give bigger prizes, like a bicycle or a new car. This might have made more people participate. We did not change the prizes during the project. If we had, it might have helped. We thought the gift cards were good, but bigger prizes might have been even better. If we had announced bigger prizes in December and January, it might have helped people stay interested.

An ETF is a security that tracks an index or a group of assets. It is like an index fund, but it trades like a stock.  An ETF gives you the good things of an index fund and the good things of owning single stocks.  You can sell short, buy on margin, and buy one share at a time.  The cost of an ETF is lower than the cost of a typical mutual fund.  But you must pay a fee for each trade.  There are many types of ETFs available.  To learn more, we will look at the ETF IHF and its top 10 holdings.  We will compare these holdings to see if owning one ETF is the same as owning many stocks.

We will look at the top 10 stocks that make up 63.58% of the ETF IHF.  These stocks are the most important ones in the fund.  We will use a chart to see how these stocks work together.

The chart shows that if we own only the top 10 stocks, we can get a return of 6.11% more than the ETF IHF.  This is a 16% increase.  The chart also shows that the risk of the top 10 stocks is lower than the risk of the ETF IHF.  It seems that owning the top 10 stocks could be a good choice.

But we need to be sure.  We will look at the standard deviation of each stock to see if the two portfolios are different.  The standard deviation is a measure of how much a stock can go up or down.  If the standard deviation is low, the stock is more stable.

Edgar Allan Poe wrote a famous poem called "Dream-Land". It is one of his best poems. Poe used a word called "Thulé" in lines 6 and 56. Thomas Mabbott found this word in the work of Virgil. Virgil used it to describe an island north of Britain. The Greeks thought it was the end of the world.

But Poe might have gotten the word from a German writer. Poe liked German writers. One writer he liked was Goethe. Goethe wrote a play called "Faust". It was a big success. It was published in two parts: the first in 1808 and the second in 1832, the year Goethe died.

In the second part of "Faust", there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé". It tells the story of a king whose wife dies. He drinks a lot and cries because he misses his wife. He decides to die too, and he gives his things to his children. He goes to a cliff and throws a special cup into the ocean. Then he dies.

The king in "The King of Thulé" is similar to the man in "Dream-Land". He is also sad and drinks a lot. Maybe Poe was thinking of Goethe's story when he wrote "Dream-Land". Goethe wrote "Faust" in 1808, and Poe used the word "Thulé" in a different poem in 1842.

Poe wrote about Thulé twice in his book. He used the phrase "ultma Thule" in "The Pit and the Pendulum", and he used it again in "Dream-Land". These two poems can be read together. In "Dream-Land", Poe describes a place called Thulé. It is a dark and lonely place where he sees dead friends and a world without color. This is similar to the story of "The King of Thulé". The king is also lonely and sad because he lost his wife.

Goethe was a famous writer, and Poe would have known his work. Poe admired another writer named Tennyson. Poe said he liked Tennyson very much. Poe probably read Goethe's work because Tennyson liked him too. Also, many people were translating Goethe's work after it was first published.

A customer slipped and fell in a grocery store in California. The customer fell on applesauce. She was injured. She wants money from the store because the manager knew about the applesauce spill but did not clean it for 30 minutes. The manager was eating dinner.

A judge will not quickly reject the customer's request for extra money. To get extra money, the customer must show that the store manager acted on purpose and did not care about the harm that could happen. The customer must also show that the manager's actions were bad.

The customer will argue that the manager should have known about the harm of not cleaning the spill. Many customers had fallen before, and the manager still did not clean the spill. The customer will say that the manager was careless.

The customer will also say that the manager did not take care of the store. Six people had fallen in the store before, and the manager did nothing.

On October 13, 2009, an employee told the manager about the applesauce spill. The manager said he was busy eating dinner. Another employee told the manager again about the spill. The manager still did not clean it. At 5:30 pm, the customer fell on the spill and got hurt.

Before the customer fell, five people had fallen in the store. The customer is suing the store for money because she is hurt. We are deciding if we should ask the judge to stop considering the extra money the customer wants.

In California, people can get extra money if the other person acted with "oppression, fraud, or malice." Malice means doing something to hurt someone on purpose or doing something that is very bad and not caring about the harm it causes.

Courts have said that someone acts with malice when they know something bad will happen and they do not try to stop it.

Four years ago I took a course about Islam at CBC.  A big question in class was: Is Islam a bad religion?  I think this question is more important now than ever.  Since 9/11, I have seen the media change from being negative about Islam to being very kind.  I don't think it was possible in 2001 for a president with a Muslim family background, like Barack Obama, to be elected.

The life of the Prophet Muhammad is interesting to me.  I learned that he was different from what I thought.  I thought he was forceful and made people change their faith.  But his biography says he was a humble person who was misunderstood.  Many people came to know the truth about him and became his followers.

I also see some similarities between the teachings of Jesus and the miracles of Muhammad.  One example is when Muhammad had little food and it became enough for forty men.  This writing makes me think the writers wanted Muhammad to seem like a humble prophet who didn't need to prove anything.  This makes me think they are trying to take credit for the life of Jesus.

The biography has many stories that seem like proof that people converted to Islam on their own.  But some of these stories are not first-hand.  They are from someone who heard from someone else.  This makes me think the stories are not true.

What bothers me most is that the writers make Muhammad seem like a kind and wise man.  But history says he was not like that.  I think Muslims do not know the real story of Muhammad's rise to power.

The ideas of Jesus and what he believed are not seen in Christian thought today.  This is because Christianity changed quickly after Jesus' life.  If we look at history, we can see that Christianity moved away from its beginning.  Today, there is a growing desire to understand Christianity better.  People are becoming more aware of the true meaning of the religion.  They want to know what was truly said by Jesus, not what was added later.  It may take a long time, but eventually people will want to go back to the original ideas of Jesus.  They will want to remove the ideas that were added later.  This will be a movement to return to the ideas of Jesus.  When this happens, the church will still be strong.  But people will believe in the same things, not many different things.  They will be more alike.  History shows that big changes can happen.  For example, the Roman Empire was against Christians, but later it became Christian.  Our country changed from slaves to leaders.  This change in Christianity will be big.  It will go back to the beginning and make people believe the same things.  To do this, people will need to understand Jesus' words in a special way.  They will not be taken as exact words.  What happened after Jesus?  A long time ago, there was only Judaism.  It was the first part of the Christian religion.  The Hebrew Bible was important, and people believed in one God.  But the Jewish people were not all the same.  They were divided into groups like Sadducees, Pharisees, and others.

The Jungle is a book. It shows how people are naturally selfish. They only think about themselves. They want their lives to be good. They do not care about others. The Jungle shows this in many ways. People in charge of big factories are selfish. They want to make their factories big and successful. They do not care about anyone or anything that gets in their way. They hurt people and the environment.

The author of The Jungle, Upton Sinclair, writes about the harm factories cause. He says, "The factories stand tall in the air. Smoke from the factories goes far away." Sinclair paints a picture of the harm pollution causes. He shows that the people in charge do not care about people or animals that get hurt.

The owners and managers also do not care about their workers. They want to make money. They make workers work long hours. They lay off workers without warning. Workers get no help finding new jobs. During the time the book was written, there were no laws to protect workers. The owners and managers were in charge. They made workers work in bad conditions.

The workers had no help. They were expected to accept the bad conditions. There were unions to help workers. But these unions often hurt the workers. They made money from the workers. Workers were very unhappy. They were like slaves. They lived on the edge of starvation. They depended on their bosses for work. The bosses were mean and unfair. This made immorality common.

F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many techniques to make readers feel a certain way about important things. He uses different techniques in his novel The Great Gatsby. One technique is to pair a word with a thing that does not usually go together. This creates a special feeling about the thing. Fitzgerald does this with colors. He uses colors to mean different things.

Fitzgerald uses the colors white and gray to mean uniformity. Uniformity is when everything is the same. White means something is nice and high class. Gray means something is old and not new. Fitzgerald uses these colors many times in the beginning of the novel to show this meaning. Many people wear white in the beginning. Daisy and Jordan wear white often. Tom wears a white shirt when he meets Myrtle. Even Nick wears white when he goes to a party. 

Fitzgerald also uses white and gray for common things. He describes the streets of New York as white. He says the names of people at a party are gray on a schedule. He says a building is a long white cake. He says some people are white or gray because they are not important. 

After Fitzgerald makes us understand the meaning of white and gray, he uses them to show that something is not important. He does this with Daisy. Fitzgerald does not use the colors white and gray for a long time, and then he uses them to make us see Daisy as not special. We see her wearing white and gray clothes, and she seems like just a part of a group. She is not special anymore.

Fitzgerald uses this technique many times to show us that Daisy is not special. He makes us see her as just a part of a group. He uses this technique to make us feel a certain way about Daisy.

A county in California called San Diego is very good for farming. The climate is warm and sunny. Many crops are grown here, including tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, and fruits from trees like peaches and lemons. The land also produces berries, honey, and peppers.

There is a lot of demand for organic food in the San Diego area. Many people want to buy food from local farms that use good methods for the earth. Some farms allow people to visit and see how they farm. Visitors can also walk or look for birds in the area.

These types of farms can help the owner get government help while keeping the land healthy. This can also create jobs and allow people to learn about farming.

Organic farming is good for the environment. It helps keep the soil and water clean. But it can be expensive. Farmers must work harder to keep pests away and to make the soil healthy without using bad chemicals. They may also lose more crops than farmers who use chemicals.

To make money from their land, farmers can use methods that help wildlife. For example, they can plant special crops to help animals and remove weeds and bad plants. This can cost more money and labor. The farmer may also need help to make sure the land is healthy and good for animals.

The land chosen for this example is near a town called Potrero in San Diego County. It is 160 acres of land with plants and trees that are not native to the area. The land is next to a forest and is in a special area where many plants and animals live. The government is looking at a plan to protect this area and its wild animals.

People have lived in this area for many years. The land was used for farming and making wood. I chose a piece of land from a website and looked at government programs that can help farmers. I also found an example of an organic farm in the same area.

Culture is very important in any talk. Culture is not just one thing. It can be what a group of people are not like and what they are. Culture is also not the same in all places. We should not say all people from a country are the same. For example, we should not say all Russians are stubborn or all Japanese are friendly. These statements are too simple.

To understand another culture, we need to know what it means to the people and how it will affect the talk. We must be patient and try to understand it. When we meet a new culture, we think of our own culture and make comparisons. To understand another culture, we can study its history, its problems, and its ideas. We should not judge or try to change a culture. We just accept it and work with it.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies also have their own culture. A company's culture can be different from another company in the same country. A company may work very long hours or have a more relaxed schedule. We can see a company's culture in how employees dress, how they communicate, and how they hire people.

It is also important to understand the values of a culture. Values are the reasons behind a culture. If a culture values harmony, a negotiator will not hurt his company's or boss's feelings to win. If a culture values hard work, a negotiator will not give up easily. We should know these values before the talk. But we also need to know the person we are talking to, so we can talk effectively.

A long time ago, a wise person said, "There is no God." This idea is from the Bible in Psalm 14. It is also the idea that Thomas Aquinas believed in. Because both St. Anselm and Thomas Aquinas write about God, we will look at their ideas. We must start by believing that God exists. If we do not, it is hard to compare their ideas. Our two authors believe in a specific God. If they believed in a different God, we could not compare their arguments.

St. Anselm's idea is that we know God is true inside our minds. We cannot think of a time when God did not exist. This idea is a way of knowing God through faith. Faith means believing something is true without needing proof. 

Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He thinks we can know God is true through reason and evidence. We do not need faith to believe in God. This would help people come to Christianity because they would be convinced by logic, not just by faith. Thomas Aquinas shows five ways to know God is true. These are: change, cause and effect, something that can be broken, degrees of perfection, and harmony. He says that if we know all the parts of a puzzle except one, we can figure out what the missing part is.

A long time ago, in the fifth or sixth century BCE, a prince was born. He would one day be called Buddha. During his life, he gave up his life in the world and became wise. His teachings created Buddhism. Over time, Buddhism changed a lot. Today, it is different from when Buddha was alive. You can see this in Sri Lanka, a country where people follow Theravada Buddhism. They have a special ceremony every year. Monks and ordinary people take part in this ceremony. It has special meaning, even though Buddha did not teach about it. The Theravada Buddhist community has changed over time. This is true for both monks and ordinary people. The community has changed its rules. This happened because of forces both inside and outside Buddhism. These forces are sometimes good and sometimes bad.

You will hear some words many times in this talk. Let's define them. An internal force is a force from inside the Buddhist community. An external force is a force from outside. A hostile force is a force that hurts Buddhism. A benign force is a force that does not want to hurt Buddhism.

First, let's talk about Buddhism. What are its basic ideas? Buddhists trust in three things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is made up of three baskets of Buddhist texts. The Sutta Pitaka has many teachings from the Buddha. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for monks and nuns. The Abhidhamma Pitaka talks about the nature of the world. It says that life is hard, things change, and we are not the same person we were before. If we understand these ideas, we can stop the cycle of death and rebirth. With enlightenment, we can stop feeling unhappy, angry, and confused. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for living. For ordinary people, there are five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not be wrong in your behavior with others, and do not take bad substances. Monks have more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, our attachments cause suffering. Third, suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico are two countries that had a long disagreement for 57 years. It started in 1836 and ended in 1893. This disagreement was the biggest between these two countries. 

The most important event in this disagreement was the Mexican-American War. It happened from 1846 to 1848. The United States won the war. They took control of Texas and the American Southwest. This made the United States a bigger country.

Many small conflicts happened between the two countries. These conflicts began to stop just before the First World War. The disagreement started because Americans and Mexicans did not agree on many things. These included religion, culture, and how they lived. They also had different economic interests.

This is like many other countries that have disagreements with their neighbors. When countries share a border, they often have problems. These problems can lead to disagreements between the countries. The United States and Mexico are like many other countries with disagreements.

David M. Pletcher said that the United States has had problems with two countries: Mexico and Cuba. These countries are close to the United States. They have been rivals to the United States for a long time.

One of the main reasons for the disagreement was religion. The United States was against the Catholic Church and monarchy. This was a problem that many countries have had in the past. The United States and Mexico did not agree on these issues.

The distrust between the two countries started from the time when the English and Spanish were rulers. The United States and Mexico were under these rulers for a long time. This distrust made it hard for them to have good relations.

Diehl and Goerts listed 17 disagreements between the United States and Mexico. Most of these disagreements were about the border. They were about raids from Mexico into the United States and other problems.

The United States and Mexico had to use their armies to stop these raids. The rivalry started to end when Mexico became dependent on the United States. The United States changed its goals from taking more land to helping Mexico economically.

Fifteen years ago, I got very sick. I was a nurse then. I chose that job because I wanted a safe and secure life. People said, "You will always find a job. People will always get sick." So, I chose nursing instead of being a scientist or a journalist.

But life changed. I am now 46 and alone. I have no money. I am still sick and cannot work. After 15 years on government help, I have nothing. Every day is hard. I am not safe. But I am not alone. My family and friends help me. I am not strong, but they help me.

I want to say that bad things can happen in life. We cannot prepare for everything. No matter how hard we try, some things are too big to handle alone.

I agree that we should not trust the government too much. But I think it is better to trust each other. We should help each other. We should ask for help when we need it.

Some people in the US talk about being strong and independent. But our ancestors were not strong on their own. They helped each other. They shared what they had.

So, be prepared. I have a special kit with food and water. I have first aid supplies and ways to make water safe to drink. I have lights and food for a long time. But it is also important to know your neighbors.

We want to know how living things change over time. What makes them change like they do? Are there rules that control how they change? In 1917, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that it is very hard to understand how living things develop using math. This is still true today.

Recently, scientists have used math to study how some animals, like mollusks, grow their shells. We are studying how math and experiments can help us understand how animals develop and change over time. We used pictures of shells to find numbers that can be used in math models. These models help us understand how shells develop.

Shells are like tubes that grow over time. They turn around in a circle, 360 degrees. The parts of the shell are called whorls. They grow around a central point, like a big line. This line is called the columella. The speed at which the whorls grow is different for each shell.

Imagine a shell as a path that moves through space over time. We can count the parts of the shell, called whorls, by drawing a line across the shell and counting the parts. We can also use math to show how the shell grows over time.

We can see shells from different angles, like from the top or the bottom. We can also look at the opening of the shell, called the aperture. To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the top and find the first line that separates the parts. Then we draw a line and count the parts.

A shell is like a path that grows over time. We can use math to show how it grows. We can also change the math to see how the shell develops. This can help us understand how animals develop and change over time.

Indonesia's baby and young child death rates are not changing much.  The country is meeting some of its goals for clean water and sanitation.  But the country is not improving fast enough in healthcare for babies and mothers.  We will talk about the reasons for this below.

One reason for this is that more mothers are getting help from healthcare workers when they give birth.  Now, 72% of births have a skilled worker present.  But this number is not as good as it seems.  Some of these workers are midwives, who cannot help if a pregnancy problem happens.  This is why many mothers are dying from severe bleeding after giving birth.  We need to do more work on this.

Another problem is that fewer children under five years old are getting medical help when they have diarrhea.  We do not have complete information on post-birth care.  But it is clear that this area is a problem.

Not enough mothers are having cesarean sections, which are needed in some cases.  In cities, 7% of births are cesareans.  But in rural areas, it is only 2%.  This is a problem because healthcare services are mainly in cities.  The rich people have better access to healthcare.  There is a big difference between the health services used by the very poor and the very rich.  It is clear that the poor are having trouble getting healthcare.

The next step to improve baby and mother health is to find a way to make healthcare more available.  We need to know if Indonesia should focus on specific programs or strengthen the whole healthcare system.  Many say that we should focus on one problem at a time.  These programs can give quick results and have clear goals.  But there are some problems with this approach.  If we give a lot of money to one program, other areas of healthcare may not get enough money.  People will go to work on the programs with the most money.

We also have a problem with many programs doing the same work.  This means we have too many forms, too much paperwork, and too many supplies.

Victorian novels are known for being very detailed and focusing on the wealthy people of that time. Two novels that are different from this style are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights. These novels use mystery and strange events to make the characters more interesting. They help us understand the characters' thoughts and feelings.

One character, Oliver, had many strange thoughts in his mind. He was still thinking about two men, Sikes and Crackit, who were arguing. Oliver heard their words and thought he was talking to them. Then, he suddenly heard gunshots and saw people crying and shouting. He felt pain and was moved quickly away. Throughout this, Oliver felt a deep and uncomfortable feeling of pain.

These novels use strange and dreamlike scenes to create mystery. In Oliver Twist, these scenes show us Oliver's inner thoughts and feelings. When Oliver is shot, he remembers the event in a dream-like way. He is trying to find help, but he feels he has no control over what is happening. Oliver is hurt and afraid, and this makes him question who is to blame for his bad luck. He did not do anything to cause his problems, so why is this happening to him? This shooting shows that Oliver has no control over his life. It also makes us think that Oliver is giving up, which is a result of the bad things that have happened to him.

The day passed quickly for Oliver. It was there and then gone. The night was long and quiet, but it was also short because it came and went fast.

A few years ago, I helped students in an after-school program. I worked one-on-one with students who needed help with their schoolwork. I was good at helping with English and reading. One student, a boy named Adrian, had trouble reading. He was in third or fourth grade. I noticed something strange. Some letters he read well, but others not at all. He spoke perfect English, but his reading was a problem.

One day, Adrian's mother came to the after-school program. She only spoke Spanish. I could not talk to her in Spanish. But we found a way to communicate. Then I understood that Adrian's problem was not that he could not read. His problem was that he did not know the English alphabet very well.

I tell this story to talk about a big problem in schools. Many students have trouble with language. This is especially true in California. But it is not always easy to see. Even students who speak perfect English can have trouble reading.

We know that this is a problem. So what do we do? For Adrian, the answer was simple. He needed help with his English reading and alphabet. But for many students, it is not that easy. There is no one solution. We need to use many methods together.

For example, we can use a program where students learn two languages. This is called a dual language system. Many people think this is a waste of resources. But it is not true. Students who use this system do better in school. If we use this system in all schools, all students will benefit.

But how do we do this? Do we need all teachers to speak two languages? No, that is not possible. But we can have special helpers who speak two languages. They can work with teachers and students to help them learn.

We are told from a young age that something is bigger than we are. Some people go to school to learn about it. Others learn from their parents.  People have different ideas about this bigger thing.  Some accept what they were taught. Others do not believe in it.  We all try to find our own way. 

One day, I asked my father about his favorite bird.  We sat on our porch during the rain.  He looked outside, thinking deeply.  He had lost weight and looked tired.  His hair was thin.  He avoided looking at me.  I was sad and scared.  I wanted to talk to him about being sad, but I was afraid it would be too hard.  So I hugged him and sat close to him.

My father died five days after my twenty-second birthday.  The medicine did not make him feel better.  He lived a few more months than the doctors thought.  I did not understand the value of that.  I thought, "What kind of God would do this?"  I did not pray at night.  If God existed, I thought he was not listening to me.

I did not want to see my father die.  I could not watch him go.  I wanted to remember him by how he lived, not how he died.  I knew my father better than anyone.  I knew he would not want me to watch him die.  So I stayed in my bed for three days.

No one called me when I was sad.  I was alone.

The Gothic Novel is a mix of old and new ideas. Ian Watt says it is an oxymoron. An oxymoron is a word that is not true, like "jumbo shrimp." The Gothic way of writing has been praised and blamed. Some people think it has no real meaning, while others say it makes you feel a strange, strong emotion (Burke). The first Gothic Novel is "The Castle of Otranto" by Horace Walpole. He used ideas from old romances and modern novels to create a new way of writing. Walpole used old theatrical ideas and new, natural descriptions to write "A Gothic Story" (Walpole 4). The Gothic way of writing uses many old things from the Middle Ages, like theater, buildings, and traditions. When "The Castle of Otranto" came out, the word "gothic" was used to describe different people, styles, and times. People thought it was old-fashioned and not sophisticated compared to modern society and literature. The combination of old and new ideas in the Gothic Novel makes it last a long time and feel both old and new to readers.

One important idea in Gothic Novels is chivalry. Chivalry is the idea of training a knight to be brave, honorable, and good. The original Gothic Novel, "The Castle of Otranto," keeps this idea and changes it. Chivalry is important to Gothic writers because it shows what a perfect knight is, and they saw a lack of that in their society. Through chivalric ideas, the past becomes ideal and romantic (like the future Romantic movement). This is used to try to make the present better. Walpole wrote "The Castle of Otranto" during a difficult time in politics. He was unhappy with the future and wrote about the good things in the past. One character, Frederic, shows these chivalric qualities. Before we meet him, we know he is a prince, has suffered, and is supposed to have been killed by enemies. He is also described as a gallant and courteous knight, but this is an exaggeration. This exaggeration is a new idea in Gothic writing, where things are taken to an extreme.

Supply chain management is the process of moving goods from customers to the finished product. This process begins with raw materials and ends with the customer getting the product. Supply chain management was created in 1982 by Keith Oliver. He explained how to plan, control, and do what is needed to please customers.

There are six important parts to a supply chain. They are production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Managers use these parts to give good service to customers.

Production is the first step. It is the base of the supply chain. Managers need to know what customers want. They look at the market to find out. The market helps them decide what customers need.

Once managers know what customers want, they can decide what products to make and how many. They also decide where to make the products and which factory is best for quality and quantity.

After that, managers plan the work and take care of the machines. Production is very important. Every detail is important. If details are not planned, it can cost the company time and money.

For example, I worked at Wal-Mart and Target. Both companies have a plan for every part of the business. They have a plan for how employees work and how to get goods from trucks. This helps the company work smoothly.

The second important part of supply chain management is supply. Supply means making decisions about what a company can do well and where to get help from other companies. A company can make many parts of a single product. Managers decide which part is best for each step. They may also send work to other companies to save time and money. This is called velocity.

Velocity means being able to make good products quickly and at a low cost. Managers use velocity to make their company better.

A sign in Burma says Hitler is alive. Ellen Page, a famous actress, stands on a street corner with a sign above her head. She is in Myanmar, a country in Southeast Asia. The government in Myanmar is very bad. They took power in 1962. People in Myanmar want freedom.

Many people in Myanmar protested in 2007. They were led by Buddhist monks. The protests were called "The Saffron Revolution." Monks wear yellow robes. The government was angry and hurt many people. They killed some journalists who came to report on the protests. One journalist from Japan was killed.

This is not new. Many governments want to be in control. They do not want people to be free. Long ago, Roman leaders thought they were gods. In Japan, the emperor is thought to be a god. In the United States, the president talks to a man who leads a group called Stupid People Worldwide.

There are many examples. In 1989, many people in China protested. They were killed by the government. Some said 200 people died, but others said 2,000 or 3,000 died. In Rwanda, a group called Hutu killed many people. They killed Tutsis and people who wanted peace. During World War II, a man named Hitler killed many Jewish people.

Duke Ellington's work in jazz is important today because he lived a long time and could create music for many years. He was a good composer who wrote music that showed what each musician could do. Ellington played the piano in some of his songs, but most of the time he wrote music for others to play. He created music that allowed soloists to be creative and play freely. He also wrote songs with strong structures and rhythms that showed off the special sound of each musician. This made his music sound new and exciting.

Ellington's music is also special because he used the voice as a jazz instrument. He started using this idea in his early music, like "Creole Love Call". This song is a slow blues that uses voice and other instruments in a special way. The song has six parts. In each part, the voice and other instruments talk to each other in a special way. This creates a rich and interesting sound.

In one part of the song, the trumpet plays a sad and slow melody. In another part, the clarinet plays a fast and exciting melody. The piano plays a special rhythm in the background. The song also has a part where the whole band plays together, and another part where the reeds play a high sound and the brass play a strong beat. The last part returns to the start, but with a special sound that is like a growl.

Ellington used his voice in another song, "Hot and Bothered". He combined his skill at writing music with his ear for sound. He used a trumpet player and a singer to create a special sound. They talked to each other in a special way, and this made the music sound rich and interesting.

In another song, "It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing)", Ellington used a trombone player to introduce the melody. The player used a special sound that was muffled, but still sounded great.

She always felt something was missing. This feeling started when she was 14 years old. It was still there at 17. She wanted someone, not just a thing. But she was not interested in any boy. Some boys liked her, but she did not feel a connection. She tried to think about why this was happening to her.

Her parents were kind and calm people. They did not argue with each other. They did not often argue with their daughter either. The only time they argued was about her wanting to be independent. She was a calm daughter, but she was also very fun and nice. People liked her.

One day, she heard a loud cry from the kitchen. It was her mother's voice. She ran to the kitchen and saw her mother on the floor. Her mother was in pain and said "Ow" many times. She helped her mother and said "Mom, I will take you to the hospital." Her mother told her where to pick her up. She was glad she had taken classes to be strong. She carried her mother to the car and drove her there.

The hospital was a place with bad smells and sickness. But she was not afraid. She helped her mother and called for doctors. The doctors came and took her mother to be looked at. Her daughter sat down and was worried.

Her mother had fallen off a stool while getting a vase from a high shelf.

This study wanted to see if eating the "Mediterranean Diet" is good for your heart.  The diet is high in plant foods, like fruits, nuts, and whole grains.  It is also high in fish and low in animal products and bad fats.  A little bit of alcohol is allowed.

Earlier studies showed that people who eat the Mediterranean Diet are less likely to die from heart disease and other heart problems.  One study showed that this diet is better than a low-fat diet for losing weight and lowering bad cholesterol.

This study followed 74,886 women from the age of 38 to 63.  They did not have heart disease or diabetes.  The women were part of a large study of 121,700 female nurses in 11 US states.  The women answered questions about their food for six times between 1984 and 2004.  They reported what they ate for a year before each time.  More than 95% of the women continued to answer the questions for 20 years.  The answers were checked with medical records.  Women who had heart disease or stroke were identified by checking their medical records or death certificates.  If there was no record, they were counted as "probably" having a heart disease or stroke.

The study also looked at things that could affect the results, like weight, smoking, and exercise.  The women were asked about these things.  To make the results more accurate, the women's answers were averaged over two years.  The study found that eating the Mediterranean Diet was associated with a lower risk of heart disease and stroke.

Women who ate the most Mediterranean foods had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke than women who ate the least.  During the 20-year study, 2391 women had heart disease, 1763 women had a stroke, and 1077 women died from heart disease or stroke.  Women who ate the most Mediterranean foods had a 29% lower risk of heart disease and stroke.

In 2007, the United States had a big financial problem. Many people lost their jobs, the housing market fell, and some big companies went bankrupt. We must ask: why did this happen? How can we stop it from happening again?

The financial crisis was caused by bad choices made by politicians. They forced banks to give loans to people who could not pay them back. The banks also sold these loans to other groups, called CDOs. When people could not pay back their loans, the banks had no money left. They then gave this problem to others, including the rest of the economy.

This started in 1999. President Clinton wanted to stay in office longer, so he made it easier for banks to lend money to people who could not afford it. This was a bad idea. The New York Times reported on this in 1999: "Fannie Mae is in trouble. It must give loans to people who do not have much money, and it must make a lot of money for its owners." The writer of this article said that Fannie Mae could have big problems in the future.

The housing market was also very complicated. Many people had loans that changed interest rates every year. These loans were called adjustable-rate mortgages. Banks also sold groups of these loans, called mortgage-backed securities. This made the economy very weak. Many people and businesses were using too much money to buy houses. When the housing prices fell, they could not pay back their loans.

In 2007, the housing prices fell. Many banks had loans that they could not sell. The top five banks in the US had $4.1 trillion in mortgage loans. This was 30% of the country's total value. Some banks, like Bear Sterns and Lehman Brothers, had big problems. They were sold cheaply, and some banks, like Goldman Sachs and Morgan Stanley, had to become regular banks with many rules.

Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac had $5 trillion in mortgage loans. In 2008, the government took control of them.

You know exposition.  It is the part of your story where you tell too much.  This can be boring.  Some writers call it Too Much Information.  They do not like it.

My readers already know the writing tip, "Show, don't tell."  But I still make mistakes.  Exposition is the bad guy that says to write about the past to get to the good parts.

Exposition is when you tell the reader what happened in simple words.  In movies, this happens when a character tells another person everything.  In stories, the author does the telling.

Let me give you an example.  A story says a woman met her husband in a place and time.  They got married in a big way.  Her husband died in front of her.  You would not want to read about this for two pages.  You would want to know more about the husband.  How did he talk?  How did he act?  You would want to know how the woman felt about him.  This would make you care about her and her husband.

As a writer, you need to add meat to the story.  This means showing, not telling.  It is hard to resist telling too much.  For example, you might introduce a new character and want to tell everything about him.  He was in the Air Force, now he works at night at a gas station, he was married twice, and he likes fishing.

I watched two news programs on August 13, 2011. The first was NBC 4. It was live. The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio. He stabbed his wife. His name is Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture. He looked very bad. The news spent two minutes on this story. They said he stabbed her many times. He was arrested.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers. He was 18 years old. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He was very sick. The police were investigating. No one was arrested yet.

I am sad to say that the news does not always talk about minority victims. If a white person is hurt, the news talks about it a lot. But if a minority person is hurt, the news does not talk about it as much.

The news also talked about a helicopter that was shot. It was a Med-Flight helicopter. A bullet hit it. The police are looking for the person who shot it. They are offering a five-thousand dollar reward.

The news also talked about the weather. There will be rain and thunderstorms on Saturday. The temperature will be around 80 degrees.

The news also talked about a store that was robbed. A man robbed a store on Clime Road. He was a black man. He wore a dark sweatshirt. I think the news talked too much about the man's color.

The news also talked about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big dealer of marijuana. He was from Texas. He was sentenced to 300 months in prison. That is 25 years. I do not know why they said it this way. They also said he is Hispanic. This does not seem important to the story.

There is a strong connection between brothers. This connection has many feelings inside: love, pride, jealousy, and anger. Brothers understand each other very well. They can see themselves in their brother. When life is very hard, the true nature of this connection is clear. This can be good or bad. When we see the true feelings, they can cost us a lot. We must understand the consequences of these feelings. When we see a brother, we see ourselves. We see how we truly are. We see our actions and their results. This shows our true character.

The story "The Scarlet Ibis" talks about this connection. Two brothers go on a difficult journey. They have bitter feelings and strong pride. In the end, only one brother lives. The story shows the feelings of the main character and his brother through their actions and words. The narrator also tells us how the main character feels and sees the world.

The main character feels one main feeling: pride. He wanted a brother to teach him things. He wanted a brother to play with. But his brother, Doodle, is very sick. He may not be able to do the things the main character wants. This makes the main character very sad. He even thinks about hurting his brother. But when his brother smiles, he feels better. This shows that he loves his brother. He wants his brother to be happy.

The brain is a very important system in our body. It helps us think and learn. In the past, people used different pictures to describe the brain. They used a piece of wax, a piece of paper, a book, and a computer. These pictures are helpful but not perfect. As we learn about the brain, we must remember that they are not always right.

The brain takes in information from our senses. Our senses are our eyes, ears, nose, tongue, and skin. They give us signals from the world around us. These signals are changed into special messages in the brain. The brain uses these messages to understand what we see, hear, and feel.

When we look at a picture, the brain breaks it down into small parts. It looks at the colors, the shape, and the edges of things. This is called bottom-up processing. The brain uses this information to say, "I see a box." Then, the brain uses the information it already knows to say, "It's a black box, not a hole in the wall." This is called top-down processing.

The brain has a special filter. It decides what information is important and what to pay attention to. For example, when you look down, you don't see every single blade of grass. But if someone calls your name, you hear it. This helps you focus on what's important.

The brain stores information in different ways. It has a special place for new information. This is called short-term memory. It also has a special place for information we keep for a long time. This is called long-term memory. When we learn something new, our brain encodes it. This means it changes the information into a special form that we can understand.

The brain keeps information safe by using special signals. These signals help us remember things for a short time. When we store information for a long time, the brain uses special proteins to keep it safe.

There are many ways to think about how the brain works. Some people think about how we remember things. Others think about how computers work. Still, others think about the brain itself. One way to think about the brain is to imagine it as a network of connections. These connections are like links between ideas. For example, if you think of a chair, you might also think of a table, wood, and other related things.

Aldous Huxley writes a story about a future world where people are not free. He calls this world Brave New World. In this world, people value group happiness above personal freedom. They are taught to be happy from a young age and not to think for themselves. 

The people in Brave New World are like pawns in a game. They are controlled by the World Controller. The World Controller tells them what to do and think. By looking at Huxley's story through a different way of thinking called Marxism, we see that Huxley is warning us about the dangers of this kind of system. 

Marxism talks about how people are controlled by those in power. Huxley uses this idea in Brave New World. He shows how people are not really in control of their own lives. They are too busy thinking about their own happiness. The people in Brave New World are like this. They are controlled by the World Controller and by the need to buy and consume things.

The people in Brave New World are divided into different groups. The lower groups, like the Delta and Gamma, do not have their own ideas. They are taught to want to buy and consume things through a special sleep-teaching method. This is controlled by the World Controller.

The upper groups, like the Alphas and Betas, are born to be in charge. But they do nothing to change the system. They just accept their place in society. This is like the idea of one group of people controlling others. The lower groups are unaware of this control and just follow what others do.

In Brave New World, people do not really connect with each other. The characters in the story are not deep or interesting. Huxley may be saying that technology and capitalism take away people's free will and expression. People do not feel strong emotions like love or sadness. They just talk about superficial things like physical appearance.

The people in Brave New World are also satisfied with their place in society. This shows how capitalism can make people accept their position in life. They are happy to obey the rules and do what others tell them to do.

I am a student at University Park. I have been here for two and a half years. Getting around campus can be hard. My freshman year, I lived in a dorm in East Halls. It was very far from my classes. I had to walk from my dorm to classes in other parts of campus. It took 25 minutes to walk to some classes. Sometimes the weather was bad, and it was even harder to walk.

Not long ago, East Halls was far from the rest of the school. There was a lot of empty land between the dorms and other buildings. Now, that empty space is filled with sports fields and new buildings. Our campus is getting bigger. It is harder to get from one place to another.

Bicycles are a good way to get around on campus. But we need more than just bicycles. The campus needs to be good for bicyclists. A man I know said he likes bicycles. He said they are the best way to get around.

I live off campus now. I have classes in Thomas building. It takes 25 minutes to walk to class. I ride my bike to class. It only takes 5 minutes. The road to class is not always easy to ride on.

Walking is also good, but I am too busy. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk to class. It would take a lot of time. I would have to walk to other classes and appointments too. It would take too much time out of my day.
